title: Get involved
---
body:

Thanks for your interest in our development and content department! Check out our "[Getting started](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/wiki/Getting-started)" article for general information on our project's development. If you are interested in contributing to Unknown Horizons, you should [join our IRC channel #unknown-horizons@irc.freenode.net](http://www.unknown-horizons.org/support/irc/) and have a chat with the community.

We've also assembled a list of open positions, i.e. areas to work on.

![Reporting Bugs](/static/buttons/base_button_bugs.png)**Reporting Bugs**

To report bugs, either file a new issue at our [bug tracker](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/issues) or post on our [forums](http://www.unknown-horizons.org/forum/)!

![Making Suggestions](/static/buttons/base_button_forums.png)**Making Suggestions**

Suggestions can be posted in our [Discussion Forum](http://www.unknown-horizons.org/forum/) or discussed with the community on [IRC](http://www.unknown-horizons.org/support/irc/).

![Updating Graphics](/static/buttons/base_button_gfx.png)**Updating Graphics**

We are always looking for new graphics! See the Information for Artists article in our wiki.

![Improving Translations](/static/buttons/base_button_i18n.png)**Improving Translations**

Want to see Unknown Horizons in your language or improve the current translation? Check out our [translation project](http://www.unknown-horizons.org/get-involved/weblate/) at Weblate!

![Hacking the Code](/static/buttons/base_button_code.png)**Hacking the Code**

Check our [Programmers Guide](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/wiki/Coders) and find out how to install from Git [Windows](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/wiki/Windows) [Linux](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/wiki/Linux) [MacOS](https://github.com/unknown-horizons/unknown-horizons/wiki/MacOS).

